Encrypt a File

python3 file_vault.py
> Choose (1/2): 1
> Enter file path: /path/to/secret.txt
> Enter password: [hidden]

Output: secret.txt.encrypted



Decrypt a File

python3 file_vault.py
> Choose (1/2): 2
> Enter file path: /path/to/secret.txt.encrypted
> Enter password: [hidden]

Output: secret.txt.decrypted
